logic_tables.name: trans_TB_MD3_AVISOS

logic_tables.name: trans_TB_MD3_AVISOS
logic_tables.column_name: Concat("";ApplySimple("CASE WHEN #0 IS NOT NULL OR #0 <> '' THEN CONCAT('') END";LINK_AVISO);"";TITLE_AVISO;"";ApplySimple("CASE WHEN #1 = 3 THEN CONCAT('') WHEN #0 = 3 THEN CONCAT('') ELSE '' END";FLAG_FIXADO;FLAG_BLOQUEAR_CONTEUDO);"";DESC_AVISO;"";ApplySimple("DBO.FN_TIME_ELAPSED(#0)";DT_AVISO);"")

logic_tables.name: trans_TB_MD3_AVISOS

logic_tables.name: trans_TB_MD3_AVISOS
